# Allowed models for this project

Only Cursor models may work on this repository.

## Allowed

- **Composer 2.5**
- **Grok 4.5** (Cursor Grok 4.5)

## Not allowed

- Any non-Cursor / third-party model (for example Claude, GPT, Gemini, or other providers)
- Any Cursor model other than Composer 2.5 and Grok 4.5

## Agent behavior

- If the current session is not using one of the allowed models, stop and tell the user to switch to Composer 2.5 or Grok 4.5 before continuing development work.
- When spawning subagents or choosing a model for a task, only select Composer 2.5 or Grok 4.5.
- Do not suggest or recommend switching to a disallowed model for work in this project.
